        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer452165939" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10590311664130341756">This book is a relentless attack on Christianity and raises a lot of good points. For instance – religious people claiming to be moral preach against condom use when AIDS is killing millions. Why are they so obsessed about abortion and not about genocide in Darfur? Why are they opposed to gun control - would Jesus carry a gun? Why do they believe so adamantly in books written centuries ago – in texts that promote slavery? <br/><br/>Sam Harris explores many of these issues and more. Religion destroys our a</span>
  <span id="freeText10590311664130341756" style="display:none">This book is a relentless attack on Christianity and raises a lot of good points. For instance – religious people claiming to be moral preach against condom use when AIDS is killing millions. Why are they so obsessed about abortion and not about genocide in Darfur? Why are they opposed to gun control - would Jesus carry a gun? Why do they believe so adamantly in books written centuries ago – in texts that promote slavery? <br /><br />Sam Harris explores many of these issues and more. Religion destroys our ability to reason and warps the soul.<br /></span>
